What it does# Control Sleep as Android with voice using Google Assistant.
Guide# Supported voice actions# The list for each voice action is not exhaustive, but the listed phrases are guaranteed to work.
Start sleep tracking# &ldquo;Hey Google, open Sleep start tracking.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, open start tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, open tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, open sleep tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show Sleep start tracking.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show start tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show sleep tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
Stop sleep tracking# &ldquo;Hey Google, open Sleep stop tracking.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, open end sleep tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, open finish tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, open end tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show Sleep stop tracking.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show end sleep tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show finish tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Hey Google, show end tracking in Sleep.&rdquo;
Open alarms list# &ldquo;Hey Google, show alarms in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, show my alarms in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, open alarms in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, open alarms list in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, show my alarms list in Sleep.&rdquo; Show your last sleep# &ldquo;Hey Google, show my last sleep in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, open my last sleep in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, show last sleep in Sleep.&rdquo; &ldquo;Hey Google, open last sleep in Sleep.&rdquo; Google Assistant on Android 15# Google routines on Android 15 must be allowed in the Google app -&gt; your account -&gt; Settings -&gt; Assistant settings -&gt; Shortcut tab -&gt; find Sleep app -&gt; Add all suggestion options -&gt; go back -&gt; add new suggestions.
